<p><b>Academia</b> is the <a href="Community" title="Community">community</a> of <a href="Student" title="Student">students</a> and <a href="Scholar" title="Scholar" class="mw-redirect">scholars</a> engaged in <a href="Higher_education" title="Higher education">higher education</a> and <a href="Research" title="Research">research</a>.</p>
